<item>
            <title>[LU-9166] missing trailing newlines in mdt/*/hsm/policy and mdd/*/changelog_mask</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9166</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;x:~# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/lustre-MDT0000/hsm/policy
NonBlockingRestore [NoRetryAction]x:~# 
x:~# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mdd/lustre-MDT0000/changelog_mask
MARK CREAT MKDIR HLINK SLINK MKNOD UNLNK RMDIR RENME RNMTO OPEN CLOSE LYOUT TRUNC SATTR XATTR HSM MTIME CTIME MIGRT x:~# 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should also add a test to sanity to check that all readable non-empty proc files have a trailing newline (except possibly for a short list of known exceptions). A missing trailing newline doesn&apos;t look nice has has been known to confuse test scripts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
